- Regular `Seichi`
  - Completely new textures for regular Seichi (had to go with smoother textures because noisy textures bring out rings on the screen (sry if I broke your bubble not seeing em)
  - Added pavement (handplaced and rotated each rock from 5 variant -> 2810 rocks in total, unified them in blender, this was a pain in the ass)
