  - Removed foilages (Bamboos, Lotuses, Lakelotuses) if its `Snowichi` or `Scorchi`
  - Changed `Ice` material
  - Removed `Blood` (bloody water) GameObject and I change the material instead of having multiple GameObjects in the Scene
  - Made sure that `Snowichi` + `Slauchi` doesn't have bloody water and bloody ice at the same time
- New Skybox (yet agane hehe)
- Added two flowers to a secondary randomly spawned pool
- Changed my AINodes like 50 times since last update
- Removed `XuMiscTools` as a dependency
- `Shork`
  - changed texture to `Blahuce`
  - now ridable [DO THIS IDIOT]
- Optimized all audio sample rates
- Optimized every single model, improved basically all of them both visually and performance-wise, got rid of a bunch of vertecies (~3Million+)
