- Removed shadow casting on models that are not important
- `Figo` recompiled `LethalCompanySeichiItems` to the newest version of the game (this should fix uchiwa not healing players)
- Changed lights behaviours (fade distance, mode, etc)
- Excluded a bunch of layers for colliders that were unnecessary
- Something happened to `Rodrigo` oh no... oh well, we have `Rodrigo2` now
